Class BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinarySearchTree<T>

  • public class BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic Binary Search Tree data structure. The T parameter must implement the Comparable interface. The tree does not have a left and right node. It uses lessNode and greaterNode in which values smaller than and values greater than the current node are stored respectively
